LightDM is a cross-desktop display manager.

Key features of LightDM are:

	* Cross-desktop - supports different desktop technologies.
	* Supports different display technologies (X, Mir, Wayland ...).
	* Lightweight - low memory usage and fast performance.
	* Guest sessions.
	* Supports remote login (incoming - XDMCP, VNC, outgoing - XDMCP,
	  pluggable).
	* Comprehensive test suite.


You must have lightdm user and group:
  groupadd -g 800 lightdm
  useradd -d /var/lib/lightdm -s /bin/false -u 800 -g 800 lightdm
